[normal]14. [bold]How should the BBC be governed, regulated and held accountable beyond 2016?[bold]15. [bold]In a constantly evolving communications environment, does a 10-year Royal Charter and Agreement with the Secretary of State, together, provide the most appropriate constitutional framework for t[bold]he BBC?[bold]IBT supports the constitutional framework of a 10-year Royal Charter and Agreement with the Secretary of State. 
